title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Naples City Councilmen on Thursday adopted a ... budget ... but only after a public hearing in which much rabble was raised....” [From the Naples Daily News, September 16, 1983. Submitted by Lynn G. Lee, Naples, Florida.]
